    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">flexible pipe body</rdfs:label>
    <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A material artifact that constitutes the multi-layer flexible body of a flexible pipe that provides pressure containment and structural flexibility in petroleum production risers or jumpers.</skos:definition>
